<template>
    <svg @click="ToogleNavMobile" :fill="IconColor" baseProfile="tiny" id="Layer_1" version="1.2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"
        :width="IconSize" :height="IconSize" xml:space="preserve" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink">
        <path
            d="M12,3c0,0-6.186,5.34-9.643,8.232C2.154,11.416,2,11.684,2,12c0,0.553,0.447,1,1,1h2v7c0,0.553,0.447,1,1,1h3  c0.553,0,1-0.448,1-1v-4h4v4c0,0.552,0.447,1,1,1h3c0.553,0,1-0.447,1-1v-7h2c0.553,0,1-0.447,1-1c0-0.316-0.154-0.584-0.383-0.768  C18.184,8.34,12,3,12,3z" />
    </svg>
</template>

<script>
    export default {
        name: 'HomeIcon',
        props: {
            size: {
                type: String,
                require: false
            },
            color: {
                type: String,
                require: false
            }
        },
        data() {
            return {
                IconSize: null,
                IconColor: null,
            }
        },
        mounted() {
            this.getSize();
            this.getColor();
        },
        methods: {
            getSize() {
                if (this.$props.size) {
                    this.IconSize = this.$props.size
                    return
                }
                this.IconSize = "30px"
                return
            },
            getColor() {
                if (this.$props.color) {
                    this.IconColor = this.$props.color
                    return
                }
                this.IconColor = "#000000"
                return
            },
            ToogleNavMobile() {
                this.$emit("ToogleNavMobile")
            }
        },
    }
</script>
